401  /**
402   * Post-JSON-mapping operation that populates the {@code messageTags} field "by hand".
403   * <p>
404   * This is a temporary hack until we have formal public support for it/improved {@code JsonMapper} capabilities so it
405   * can handle arbitrary Map types.
406   *
407   * @param jsonMapper
408   *          The {@code JsonMapper} that was used to map to this type.
409   * @since 1.6.11
410   */
411  @JsonMappingCompleted
412  protected void jsonMappingCompleted(JsonMapper jsonMapper) {
413    if (rawMessageTags != null) {
414      messageTags = createTags(rawMessageTags, jsonMapper);
415    }
416    if (rawStoryTags != null) {
417      storyTags = createTags(rawStoryTags, jsonMapper);
418    }
419  }
420
421  private List<MessageTag> createTags(String rawTags, JsonMapper jsonMapper) {
422    try {
423      return jsonMapper.toJavaList(rawTags, MessageTag.class);
424    } catch (FacebookJsonMappingException je) {
425    }
426    // message tags not in Graph API 2.5 format, ignore this exception and try another way
427    try {
428      List<MessageTag> resultList = new ArrayList<>();
429      JsonObject rawMessageTagsObject = jsonMapper.toJavaObject(rawTags, JsonObject.class);
430      for (String key : rawMessageTagsObject.names()) {
431        String tagArrayString = rawMessageTagsObject.get(key).toString();
432        resultList.addAll(jsonMapper.toJavaList(tagArrayString, MessageTag.class));
433      }
434      return resultList;
435    } catch (FacebookJsonMappingException je) {
436      return new ArrayList<>();
437    }
438  }
